{"lemma":"خِتامٌ","slug":"خِتامٌ","root":"خ.ت.م","root_slug":"خ-ت-م","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ت-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خِتام","root":"ختم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10006","n10007"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%90%D8%AA%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of خَتَمَ (ḵatama) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of خَتَمَ (ḵatama) (form I); end, conclusion, completion"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of خَتَمَ (ḵatama)."},"ipa":["/xi.taːm/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10006","headword_ar":"خَتَامٌ","root":"xtm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the last sentence of the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10007","headword_ar":"خِتَامٌ","root":"xtm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of 1 [q. v.]. (Lh, K.) ―         -b2-  And a subst. signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first watering of seedproduce,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a sown field:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"turning up the earth over sown seed, and then watering it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Et-Táïfee, TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtimN","text_ar":"خَاتِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clay,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K,) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wax,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one seals,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stamps,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon a writing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is sealed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stamped, upon a writing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xatamN","text_ar":"خَتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". And see an ex. in a verse of Lebeed cited in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dkn","text_ar":"دكن"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  (tropical:)  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hymen;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as being the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seal of virginity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuf~ato A_ilayoka bixitaAmihaA","text_ar":"زُفَّتْ اـِلَيْكَ بِخِتَامِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She was conducted as a bride to thee with her seal of virginity"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rab~ihaA","text_ar":"رَبِّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bixaAtami","text_ar":"بِخَاتَمِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the seal of her Lord"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And [hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siyqato","text_ar":"سِيقَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hadiy~atuhumo A_ilayohi bixitaAmihaA","text_ar":"هَدِيَّتُهُمْ اـِلَيْهِ بِخِتَامِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [if it mean, as I suppose it to do,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Their present was sent to him with what rendered it perfect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"complete,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with what appertained to it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"furthest part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a valley. (JK, TA.) (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"last"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a company of men; (Lh, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtimN","text_ar":"خَاتِمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) whence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~abiy~iyna","text_ar":"النَّبِيِّينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamu","text_ar":"خَاتَمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The last of the prophets"},{"kind":"text","text":"], in the Kur [xxxiii. 40]; accord. to one reading, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtum","text_ar":"خَاتُم","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAtmu AlA^anobiyaA='i","text_ar":"خاتمُ الاَنْبِيَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. Mohammad; (S;) also called ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxaAtamu","text_ar":"الخَاتَمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxaAtimu","text_ar":"الخَاتِمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"last portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything that is drunk [&c.]. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xitaAmuhu misokN","text_ar":"خِتَامُهُ مِسْكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [lxxxiii. 26], means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The last"},{"kind":"text","text":"that they will perceive"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"will be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the odour of musk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or, accord. to 'Alkameh and Mujáhid,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its admixture"},{"kind":"text","text":"shall be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"musk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to Ibn-Mes'ood,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its result"},{"kind":"text","text":"shall be the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taste of musk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"Fr says, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtimN","text_ar":"خَاتِمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xitaAmN","text_ar":"خِتَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are nearly the same in meaning; whence the reading of 'Alee,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misokN","text_ar":"مِسْكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamuhu","text_ar":"خَاتَمُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": and the explanation is this; that when any one shall drink thereof, he will find the last cup thereof to have the odour of musk: Er-Rághib says that the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the end,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the last draught,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what shall remain, thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"shall be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in perfume"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"musk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and that the assertion that it means it shall be sealed with musk is nought. (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtimapN","text_ar":"خَاتِمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A3-  Also, (IAar, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtimN","text_ar":"خَاتِمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or, accord. to IAar, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xataAmN","text_ar":"خَتَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) sings. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xutumN","text_ar":"خُتُمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"places of separation"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuSuwS","text_ar":"فُصُوص"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the joints"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafaASil","text_ar":"مَفَاصِل"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of horses."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaA^otamN","text_ar":"خَاْتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtimN","text_ar":"خَاتِمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) which is more commonly known than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, [but see what follows,]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtaAmN","text_ar":"خَاتَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiytaAmN","text_ar":"خِيتَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K, the last in the CK and TA ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayotaAm","text_ar":"خَيْتَام","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":") and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xitaAmN","text_ar":"خِتَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K and TA but omitted in the CK) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xatamN","text_ar":"خَتَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, IHsh, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xatomN","text_ar":"خَتْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ez-Zeyn El-'Irákee, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayotamo","text_ar":"خَيْتَمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-Málik, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayotuwmN","text_ar":"خَيْتُومٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(EzZeyn El-'Irákee, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtiyaAmN","text_ar":"خَاتِيَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) signify the same; (JK, S, Msb, K, TA;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A signet;"},{"kind":"text","text":"generally"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a signet-ring;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain ornament"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloYN","text_ar":"حَلْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the finger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) app., at the first,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used for sealing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stamping, therewith;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so that the word is of the same class as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbaEN","text_ar":"طَابَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": afterwards, in consequence of frequency of usage, applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one not used for that purpose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a ring having a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faS~","text_ar":"فَصّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a substance different therefrom"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"set in it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a stone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gem, set in it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: if without a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faS~","text_ar":"فَصّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", it is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fataxapN","text_ar":"فَتَخَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtimN","text_ar":"خَاتِمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agent"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. the person"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sealing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stamping"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (JK, Az, Msb:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing that is put upon the piece of clay"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wax, for the purpose of sealing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stamping"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Az, Msb, K:) the pl. [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtimN","text_ar":"خَاتِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawaAtimN","text_ar":"خَوَاتِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and [properly of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtaAmN","text_ar":"خَاتَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawaAtiymu","text_ar":"خَوَاتِيمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, in which the former pl., though more common, is not mentioned, and K:) Sb says that those who use the latter pl. make it to be pl. of a sing. of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEaAlN","text_ar":"فَاعَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", though it be not in their language; which shows that he knew not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtaAmN","text_ar":"خَاتَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xatomN","text_ar":"خَتْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xutuwmN","text_ar":"خُتُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A seal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stamp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mark:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in a trad., in which it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=miyna xaAtamu rab~i AlEaAlamiyna EalaY EibaAdihi Almuw^ominiyna","text_ar":"ا=مِينَ خَاتَمُ رَبِّ العَالَمِينَ عَلَى عِبَادِهِ المُوْمِنِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=miyna","text_ar":"ا=مِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Amen"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the seal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stamp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the mark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the Lord of the beings of the whole world upon his servants the believers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] which removes from them accidents, and causes of mischief; for the seal of the writing protects it, and precludes those who look from [seeing] what is within it. (TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xitaAmN","text_ar":"خِتَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in seven places. [It is nearly syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xitaAmN","text_ar":"خِتَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as Fr says: and thus,] it signifies also, (JK, K,) and so does ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtimapN","text_ar":"خَاتِمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"end,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"last part"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"result,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"issue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) of a thing (JK, S, K) of any kind: (JK, K:) ↓ the latter [particularly] signifies (assumed tropical:)  the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"last part"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Msb) of a chapter of the Kur-án, (JK,) and of the Kur-án itself: (Msb:) [and (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a concluding chapter"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"section: an epilogue:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an appendix:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxotatamN","text_ar":"مُخْتَتَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [in like manner] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufotataHN","text_ar":"مُفْتَتَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aHomiydu","text_ar":"التَّحْمِيدُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufotataHu A@loquroA=ni wa A@liAsotiEaA*apu muxotatamuhu","text_ar":"مُفْتَتَحُ ا@لْقُرْا=نِ وَ ا@لِاسْتِعَاذَةُ مُخْتَتَمُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The declaration of the praises of God is the opening portion of the Kur-án, and the prayer for the protection of God is its closing portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (A, TA;) and it is a chaste word, of frequent occurrence, though the contr. has been asserted. (TA.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aEomaAlu bixawaAtiymihaA","text_ar":"الاَعْمَالُ بِخَوَاتِيمِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Actions"},{"kind":"text","text":"are characterized, or to be judged, as good or evil,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by their results"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  Also, i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of a mare, (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaloqapu Ald~unoyaA","text_ar":"الحَلْقَةُ الدُّنْيَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity, in which is the orifice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqataA Alr~aHimi","text_ar":"حَلْقَتَا الرَّحِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloqapu Ald~uburi","text_ar":"حَلْقَةُ الدُّبُرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlq","text_ar":"حلق"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tuboyap","text_ar":"طُبْيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[evidently here used as a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuboY","text_ar":"طُبْى"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"teat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"though I do not find it mentioned in its proper art. in any lexicon; unless"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino TuboyatihaA","text_ar":"مِنْ طُبْيَتِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"be a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn TuboyihaA","text_ar":"من طُبْيِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K, TA:) so called by way of comparison [to a signet or seal]. (TA.) ―         -b5-  And (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqorap","text_ar":"نُقْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the back of the neck;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K, TA;) which is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cuppingplace."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-  And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"least"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaH","text_ar":"وَضَح"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the legs"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of horses;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a slight whiteness in the parts next the hoof, less than what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxodiymN","text_ar":"تَخْدِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","TA","S","K","IAar","Msb","ISd","IHsh","Az"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}